## Variant comparison — picked: **{{ build.chosen_variant }}**

Maxroll's planner ships several progression variants per build. We score each on three heuristic axes (Damage / Survive / Sustain, 0-100, *between-variant comparison only*) using item power, world tier, gear-slot count, and unique-item count. The best composite wins — that's the variant detailed in this report.

| Variant | Lvl | wTier | Slots | Uniques | Avg pwr | Damage | Survive | Sustain | **Composite** |
|---------|----:|------:|------:|--------:|--------:|-------:|--------:|--------:|--------------:|
{%- for s in build.variant_scores | sort(attribute='composite', reverse=true) %}
| {% if s.name == build.chosen_variant %}**{{ s.name }} ◀**{% else %}{{ s.name }}{% endif %} | {{ s.level }} | {{ s.world_tier }} | {{ s.slots_filled }} | {{ s.uniques_count }} | {{ "%.0f"|format(s.avg_item_power) }} | {{ "%.1f"|format(s.damage) }} | {{ "%.1f"|format(s.survive) }} | {{ "%.1f"|format(s.sustain) }} | **{{ "%.1f"|format(s.composite) }}** |
{%- endfor %}

_Composite = 0.5·Damage + 0.3·Survive + 0.2·Sustain. The "Skill Progression" variant scores 0 because it carries no gear — it's a documentation aid, not a playable loadout._

